item.description: Boston's #1 Americana Country Music duo perform at Paradise Cafe on Oct 12th - Catch the Award winning duo performing their unique and exciting brand of Americana music. Fresh off a national tour, and opening up for the likes of Neko Case, The Avett Brothers and the New England Americana Festival - you will love the close harmonies of the duo that shine through in their rousing live performances.
item.name: Adela & Jude @ Paradise Cafe Dedham, Ma
